overview.en: CSM created by Internet + agriculture represents a new economic form, it refers to rely on the Internet information technology to realize the combination of the Internet and traditional industries, to optimize the production factors, update, and Internet + value-add new agricultural science and technology industry is undoubtedly the most emerging trends, the traditional agricultural planting to innovate, to agricultural planting industry to the rapid development of science and technology in the industry and you by my side processing of believes that science and technology, people will soon through the Internet by mobile phone can get agricultural planting bring convenience and happy, this is not only the performance of the scientific development, it is an innovation of human civilization.
overview.zh: CSM创造的互联网+农业代表的一种新的经济形态，它指的是依托互联网信息技术实现互联网与传统产业的联合，以优化生产要素、更新业务，而互联网+区块化新农科技产业无疑是当下最新兴的发展趋势，把传统农耕种植业进行创新，将农耕种植产业带到身处工业科技飞速发展中你我的身边，羿伯科技坚信，在不久以后人们将通过互联网通过手机就能感受到农耕种植带来的便捷和快乐，这不仅仅是科学发展的表现，这更是一场人类文明的革新。
